titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on tefluthrin.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 7/29/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on (2,3,5,6-tetrafluoro-4-methylphenyl)-methyl-(1a3a)- (Z)-(+)-3-(2-chloro-3,3,3-trifluoro-1-propenyl)- 2,2-dimethylcyclopropanecarboxylate (tefluthrin).
